{"tid":686552,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求指點] [貓奴] 我隻貓中意食貓砂 可以點?","createTime":"2018-06-01T11:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T14:19:07.000Z","uid":126195,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d234dc51e6d8d7eb0db1ec66ecf2044283ed04e","tid":686552,"uid":126195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"我個隻主子系男 家貓, 已經10幾歲<br />\n主要食罐頭濕糧，有時都會比D乾糧過口癮，<br />\n貓砂系用豆腐砂, 都用左好耐，近呢一個月發現已經食完濕糧之後，周不時走去食+lam d貓砂<br />\n<br />\n之前睇過網上有人話食貓砂有機會系貧血/肚漲-&gt;塞腸, 但見佢如廁正常，食慾無變都仲好大食下 成日R乾糧食...唔會淨系飲水<br />\n我都好擔心, 究竟點解會咁呢? 長期落去會唔會消化唔到/情況惡劣, 有無辦法解決? 求指點"},{"pid":"db5e83c5ac2a9da36e35d5314cdb0c97c093d13b","tid":686552,"uid":78282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"換過隻貓沙咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1aa8f34cfb83efb521c77c937c2eb887a84969","tid":686552,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:37:05.000Z","msg":"10歲都算大年紀 你會唔會帶佢教個身體檢查"},{"pid":"fd1be4c70de1eb9ee8faf3d2e821280369ae566d","tid":686552,"uid":126195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db5e83c5ac2a9da36e35d5314cdb0c97c093d13b","tid":686552,"uid":78282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"換過隻貓沙咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"我怕換左都系會照食, 如果其他物料嘅砂會塞咪大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f53efdcd715f3f6a512e36242ac38554895e40","tid":686552,"uid":78282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1be4c70de1eb9ee8faf3d2e821280369ae566d","tid":686552,"uid":126195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db5e83c5ac2a9da36e35d5314cdb0c97c093d13b","tid":686552,"uid":78282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"換過